), Algeria (new record) (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F7380954" captionText="Figure 5. Map of the distribution of Platymetopius notatus at global scale." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.9.e71418.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/575487" pageId="0" pageNumber="71418">5</figureCitation>
